body":"듣고 보니 리사가 한 말도 일리가 있어……\n……알았어.\n할로윈 이벤트에 참가할게.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":21,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":21,"voiceId":"event20-03-035","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":24}],"windowDisplayName":"아코","body":"해냈다~!\n감사합니다!\n유키나 씨!!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":24,"motionName":"gattsu01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":24,"voiceId":"event20-03-036","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":24}],"windowDisplayName":"아코","body":"의상도 제대로 준비해놨으니까\n안심하세요!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":24,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":24,"voiceId":"event20-03-037","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":21}],"windowDisplayName":"유키나","body":"의상……?\n무슨 말이야?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":21,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":21,"voiceId":"event20-03-038","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":24}],"windowDisplayName":"아코","body":"할로윈 이벤트라서 변장할 거예요.\n아코는 타락 천사를 모티브로 한 변장이고\n유키나 씨한테는 고양이 귀랑 고양이 꼬리를 달아드리려고요!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":24,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":24,"voiceId":"event20-03-039","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":21}],"windowDisplayName":"유키나","body":"고양이 귀랑…… 고양이 꼬리……?\n내가 그걸 한다는 거야……?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":21,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":23,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":21,"voiceId":"event20-03-040","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":24}],"windowDisplayName":"아코","body":"네, 맞아요!\n고양이로 변장해서 언니한테 이겨봐요!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":24,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":24,"voiceId":"event20-03-041","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"리사","body":"좋네, 좋네. 고양이 귀.\n어쩌면 앞으로 Roselia에서\n그런 의상을 입게 될지도 모르잖아?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event20-03-042","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"리사","body":"그러니까 그거 연습한다고 생각해봐, 알았지♪","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event20-03-043","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":21}],"windowDisplayName":"유키나","body":"……잘 모르겠어.\n그런 의상을 앞으로 Roselia에서 입을지도 모른다니……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":21,"motionName":"pui01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":21,"voiceId":"event20-03-044","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":24}],"windowDisplayName":"아코","body":"유키나 씨, 안 입어주실 건가요……?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":24,"motionName":"cry01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":24,"voiceId":"event20-03-045","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":21}],"windowDisplayName":"유키나","body":"…………하아.\n알았어.\n아코가 고른 의상을 입을게.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":21,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":21,"voiceId":"event20-03-046","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":24}],"windowDisplayName":"아코","body":"와아~!\n감사합니다. 유키나 씨